ate growth advice to the chairman and chief executive level members of various firms mr phillips is also managing partner of phillips international law group pllc a worldwide recognized international law firm specializing in mergers acquisitions project development and epc construction work with a focus on the international energy landscape in the oil gas chemical and power downstream sector and the alternative energy industry mr phillips clients include worldwide energy companies including several middle east national oil companies prior to his founding of bilateral initiatives llp and the phillips international law group mr phillips was a partner at the law firm of jackson walker llp from may  until may  and chaired several of the firms practice areas over that period prior to working at jackson walker llp from may  to may  mr phillips served as a chief executive officer in the former keyspan energy corporation a  billion public energy conglomerate based in new york city and as a member of the board of directors of certain keyspan subsidiaries from june  to may  mr phillips served as chief executive officer in equitable resources inc equitable a  billion public gas utility holding company based in pittsburgh pennsylvania and as a member of the board of directors of certain of equitables subsidiaries mr phillips also served as the general counsel to eastex energy inc a public midstream energy company from june  to may  which was later acquired by el paso energy and ultimately enterprise products lp in addition to his current roles at bilateral initiatives llp and phillips international law group pllc mr phillips is the chairman of the board of directors and the executive board of advisors ambassadors ministers  former us cabinet secretaries of the bilateral us arab chamber of commerce mr phillips received his bachelors degree from the university of texas in august  and his juris doctor from the south texas college of law in august  mr phillips is a member of the state bar of texas international bar association american bar association and the houston bar association he is also a member of the oil gas  energy law section the business law section and the corporate counsel section of the state bar of texas and houston bar association additionally he is a member of the natural resources energy and environmental law section of the american bar association  international bar association director qualifications mr phillips has had a long and successful career in the energy sector serving in various capacities having been the ceo legal counsel and board member of various large public companies in addition to his extensive experience in oil and gas he was also a partner in the law firm of jackson walker llp mr phillips background brings insights into corporate structure and project development along with expansion and corporate growth source vertex energy inc on  ¬† sign up for equilar atlas and view david l phillipss full profile by accessing equilar atlas you can view bios network salary and wealth events of industryleading executives like david l phillips more specifically youll be able to identify corporate executives in david l phillipss network and community follow changes in david l phillipss employment and moneyinmotion connect with david l phillips through your network of conections view full profile ¬† search for over  executive profiles bio example david l phillips david l phillipss connections  sign up now to view david l phillipss  connections ¬ª chris carlson chief financial officer and secretary vertex energy inc john strickland former chief operating officer vertex energy inc timothy c harvey board member vertex energy inc donald i moritz former board member eqt corporation benjamin p cowart chairman of the board president and chief executive officer vertex energy inc sam p cortez board member delta apparel inc matthew lieb former vice president specialty projects vertex energy inc greg wallace former vice president re